<item>
            <title>[LU-19641] lfs getstripe should not give lhm_pattern: hsm for foreign component</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19641</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Here is an output example of a foreign component for PCC :&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
$&#160;lfs getstripe /lustre/PCC
/lustre/exafs/client/HSM
&#160; lcm_layout_gen: &#160; &#160;2
&#160; lcm_mirror_count: &#160;2
&#160; lcm_entry_count: &#160; 2
&#160; &#160; lcme_id: &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; 65537
&#160; &#160; lcme_mirror_id: &#160; &#160; &#160;1
&#160; &#160; lcme_flags: &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;init
&#160; &#160; lcme_extent.e_start: 0
&#160; &#160; lcme_extent.e_end: &#160; EOF
&#160; &#160; &#160; lmm_stripe_count: &#160;1
&#160; &#160; &#160; lmm_stripe_size: &#160; 1048576
&#160; &#160; &#160; lmm_pattern: &#160; &#160; &#160; raid0
&#160; &#160; &#160; lmm_layout_gen: &#160; &#160;0
&#160; &#160; &#160; lmm_stripe_offset: 3
&#160; &#160; &#160; lmm_objects:
&#160; &#160; &#160; - 0: \{ l_ost_idx: 3, l_fid: [0x300000401:0xc3:0x0] }

&#160; &#160; lcme_id: &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; 131074
&#160; &#160; lcme_mirror_id: &#160; &#160; &#160;2
&#160; &#160; lcme_flags: &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;init
&#160; &#160; lcme_extent.e_start: 0
&#160; &#160; lcme_extent.e_end: &#160; EOF
&#160; &#160; &#160; lhm_magic: &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; 0x0BD70BD0
&#160; &#160; &#160; lhm_pattern: &#160; &#160; &#160; hsm
&#160; &#160; &#160; lhm_length: &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;56
&#160; &#160; &#160; lhm_type: &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;0x00000003 (pccro)
&#160; &#160; &#160; lhm_flags: &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; exists,archived,pccro,0x109
&#160; &#160; &#160; lhm_archive_id: &#160; &#160;0
&#160; &#160; &#160; lhm_archive_ver: &#160; 0
&#160; &#160; &#160; lhm_archive_uuid: &#160;&apos;&apos;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Foreign component are used for S3 PCC and POSIX but not HSM.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Since hsm mechanisms are not using foreign component yet, we should have :&lt;br/&gt;
    lhm_pattern: &#160; &#160; &#160;  foreign&lt;/p&gt;</description>
